question: Koh chiat nien "net loss on extinguishments of long-term debt" si loh si chin tuid?
2011 ni ni 2015, 'amortization of intangibles' ( 1 a ) ji̍t-liōng sī thong sèng sò·-chē?
Tī 'hui-kim hû-sū kòe-thêng ê thun-chîh' siōng-kóan ê nî-tāi, net income sī siáⁿ-chē?
Koh-tōa-sè lâi kóng, 2011 nî kàu 2015 nî, hō͘ lâng chai-iáⁿ ê 'non-gaap net income' ê chū-liōng ê kòe-têng chūnn-chún àn-chóaⁿ?
answer: Chhūnn-chún ê 'non-gaap net income' tī gō͘-tang ê sî-kan lāi, chin cheng-chha̍t chāi cheng-tióng, chiūⁿ-thiⁿ chiūⁿ, tùi 2011 nî ê $198.8 pah-bān kàu 2015 nî ê $503.5 pah-bān.

question: Oaⁿ-tiâu ū sîn-châi hāng-bo̍k ê lô-chiâⁿ, tī 2015 nî ê kè-chiâⁿ pí 2014 nî koân, chiap-siū 2014 nî bô-sò·-jī ê hāng-bo̍k.
answer: aggregate adjustment for income taxes ( f )

question: Tī 2015 nî, hiah "net income" sī "non-gaap net income ( g )" ê toā-khò͘ siáⁿ-chē phiah? Chhú chi̍t-ê sió-siáⁿ hō͘ jīm-hô chi̍t-ê sió-siáⁿ.

Nāi siūⁿ 'non-gaap net income' sī 'net income' kap só͘-ū tiau-chéng ê chóng-ha̍p, nā 2013 nî ê 'amortization of intangibles ( a )' nā-sī i hit nî ê siah 10%, 'non-gaap net income' ē-sī siáⁿ-mih? (tan-gîn bān)
Tùi 2011 kàu 2015 ê chu-liāu lâi kóng, 'sûn-lī' hām 'bô-GAAP sûn-lī ( g )' chi kan ū sím-khoán ê chheng-bêng koan-hē?
answer: Koh-tōa hūn ê 'sûn-lī' hām 'bô-GAAP sûn-lī' chi kan ū hui-siông chha̍t ê tīn-chhiok koan-hē. Tī chi̍t ê gō͘-liân ê kî-kan, chiū-chāi 'sûn-lī' tùi $17.1 pah-bān kàu $403.1 pah-bān tòe-tòe chē, 'bô-GAAP sûn-lī' iā tòe-tòe chē tùi $198.8 pah-bān kàu $503.5 pah-bān, ē-sái kóng nn̄g ê sū-chéng lóng ēng kāng chi̍t ê hong-hiòng.

question: Hiah-ê hāng-mū ê sū-bī-chū bē-tàng tī 2011 chì 2014 nî-kan ê chi̍t-ê í-siōng ê nî-sò͘ ū hui-sèlù-sò͘ ê tāi-bé ê?
answer: non-cash equity-based compensation related to equity investment ( b )
gain on remeasurement of equity investment ( d )

question: Gán-tsònn ê nî ū “lān-tiâu-sìng si-chha tōa-khuáⁿ chè-chè (net loss on extinguishments of long-term debt)” hō͘ tùi hit-kî-kan ê pa̍t-ê nî lâi-kóan chin tōa-chiáⁿ ê hō͘-seng, sī-în-chóan?
answer: 2011 nî ū chi̍t ê hui-siông tōa ê “lān-tiâu-sìng si-chha tōa-khuáⁿ chè-chè” ê kè-siàu. Si-chha sī $118.9 pah-bān, siáⁿ-chē pí pa̍t-ê nî lóng chin tōa, pí tē-it koân ê kè-siàu ($90.7 pah-bān tī 2014 nî) lóng chhiau-kóe 30% koh-koh pí tē-it-té ê kè-siàu ($17.2 pah-bān tī 2012 nî) kāng-khuáⁿ lóng chhiau-kóe 7 pái.

question: Tī 2011 chì 2015 nî kî-kan, ài hō͘-chò "non-GAAP net income" ê sêng-pâi sī ch how iâⁿ, koh ū siáⁿ-siáⁿ ê kiám-chiap chiâⁿ chò chit-ê piàn-tōng ê chú-iàu goân-in?
answer: Non-GAAP net income tùi 2011 nî ê $198.8 pah-bān kiám-chiap kàu 2015 nî ê $503.5 pah-bān. Chú-iàu ê kiám-chiap kiâⁿ-iâⁿ pau-koat amortization of intangibles, non-cash equity-based compensation, net loss on extinguishments of long-term debt, kap aggregate adjustment for income taxes, chit-ê sī chiap chhiok hō͘ net income lâi tit-kàu non-GAAP ê sò͘-chè.
